metadata.name: Chromatic Emanations: Goldpunk Abstraction
metadata.description:
Oh, art of now, so contemporary, 
With flowfields born of color's revelry. 
Pale azure, a whispering hue so light, 
Deep Sky Blue, a vastness free from blight. 

Columbia blue, a steadfast shade of truth, 
Green Blue, a merging of earth and youth. 
And lastly, Carnation pink, a tender bloom,
Softening the palette with sweet perfume. 

Together, they blend in harmony, 
A symphony of hues for all to see. 
Oh, how this art doth soothe my soul, 
In its beauty, I am made whole.
